Proposed law provides for an employee to file a grievance within 24 months after a violation
occurred if the employee believes that his rights were restrained, violated, denied, or
otherwise discriminated against.
Proposed law provides for a severability clause.
Proposed law creates the "Paid Parental Leave For Educators Fund".
